title: Europe considers Syria chemical attack response
text:
Europe considers Syria chemical attack response 9:18pm IST - 01:27 
European leaders are considering whether or not to join the United States in a proposed missile strike on Syria, in the wake of an alleged chemical gas attack blamed on Bashar al-Assad's government, ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
